dc_description_s: Relief shown pictorially. Fortifications colored. Includes indexes of "Nomenclature des Rues" -- "Bureaux Principaux" -- "Passages." Includes list of government departments, libraries, and theaters. 1 map: hand col., mounted on cloth; 56 x 86 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
